data.description: WOW! Stunning 2-story home in North Fork, near Pine Creek HS! This beautiful Vantage Home is like NEW, but even BETTER! The popular Carlton II floorplan has a FOUR-car garage, SIX beds, FOUR baths (including a main level bedroom and ¾ bath)! You’ll love the newly remodeled kitchen with gorgeous granite with island seating, the high-end Samsung Black Stainless appliances, double oven, gas range, upgraded pantry with wood shelves and new modern barn door, tiled mud room with new cabinets/countertops! Kitchen opens to eat-in nook and the large great room with beautiful stoned, gas fireplace – creating a warm, open feel! Main level features a separate dining room at front of home, which could also be used as a study or formal sitting area, whatever works best for your lifestyle! Upper level includes the spacious primary suite with beautiful 5-piece ensuite with quartz countertop, sleek freestanding shower and walk-in closet, plus 3 more bedrooms and tiled laundry room. Home has been upgraded galore with fully finished basement with rec room, stoned wall wet bar and fireplace with floating shelves, gas fireplace, luxury vinyl plank flooring, an additional bedroom, 3/4 bathroom, another room perfect for gym/work out area, craft or playroom. Additional home improvements include: New AC/Humidifier, Radon Mitigation system, New Paint, New Carpet, Updated Modern Lighting throughout the home, all countertops are granite or quartz! The 4-car garage is insulated and features metal overhead shelving for additional storage plus 50 amp RV outlet and holiday lighting hookup. Exterior of the home is low-maintenance stucco. Enter from adorable covered front porch! Walkout from kitchen to composite deck and enjoy the fully fenced backyard, with natural gas line to deck for BBQ and to firepit (never a need for propane). Relax in the Hottub and unwind under the pretty Colorado sky!Home backs to Walking Trail/Open Space! Move-in Ready!Welcome Home!
